
<purchabr>UNION MINIERE</purchabr> TAKES STAKE IN <acqabr>PANCONTINENTAL</acqabr>
    BRUSSELS, March 27 - {<purchaser>Union Miniere SA</purchaser>} said in a statement
that it has <status>acquired</status> an eight pct interest in <acquired>Pancontinental
Mining Ltd</acquired> {<acqabr>PANA.S}</acqabr> for a sum equivalent to <dlramt>1.2 billion Belgian
francs</dlramt>.
    <acqabr>Pancontinental</acqabr> operates <acqbus>gold and coal mines</acqbus> in <acqloc>Australia</acqloc>
and <acqbus>natural gas and oil fields</acqbus> in <acqloc>Canada</acqloc>.
    <purchabr>Union Miniere</purchabr> said the location of its interest within the
<acqabr>Pancontinental</acqabr> group will be decided later. It did not
